NAME        WINMCHK
DESCRIPTION 'WIN-MCP Hook DLL — Journal Record/Playback'
EXETYPE     WINDOWS
LIBRARY
CODE        PRELOAD MOVEABLE DISCARDABLE
DATA        PRELOAD MOVEABLE SINGLE
HEAPSIZE    1024
EXPORTS
    JournalRecordProc   @1
    JournalPlaybackProc @2
    StartRecord         @3
    StopRecord          @4
    StartPlayback       @5
    StopPlayback        @6
    GetRecordCount      @7
    GetPlaybackState    @8
    SetPlaybackSpeed    @9
    GetEventBuffer      @10
    SetEventBuffer      @11
    GetBufferCapacity   @12
